            <lg xml:id="TK1110">
<l>aṟitō ṟaṟiyāmai kaṇṭaṟṟāl kāmam </l>
<l>ceṟitōṟuñ cēyiḻai māṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As (one's) ignorance is discovered the more one learns, so does repeated intercourse with a well-adorned female (only create a desire for more).</l>
            </lg>
